{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"뭐? 그럼…… 다른 빵?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"episode116-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"저 그게…… 저번 생일 라이브의 감사 인사를\n전하려고 왔어. 간식으로 빵도 챙겨주고\n여러 가지로 도와줘서 고마워.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"odoodo02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"episode116-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"감사……?\n아하하, 됐어됐어. 그렇게 새삼스럽게 말하면 쑥스럽잖아~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"episode116-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"으응, 정말 기뻤으니까!\n초코 소라빵도 맛있었고…… 그리고……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"episode116-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"안녕~ 사~야!\n어